onstraints. to overcome the deficiencies of\nthe Stabilizers, method of Optimal Stability Control is proposed to complete\nthe solution. Simulations show that the proposed approach for stabilization of\nbiped walkers provides us with a more robust solution compared to traditional\napproaches and maximally guarantee the stability of walkers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 May 2019 03:15:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-07"}
